room_title: Escape room "Brandon's Totally Tubular Bedroom" by Escape Room Adventures in Fort Myers
room_address: 12995 South Cleveland Ave, Suite 217, Ft Myers, FL 33907
room_description: Instead of setting up a lemonade stand like all the other kids, 12-year-old Brandon has rigged his bedroom with puzzles using his toys from 1988. Can your group outwit a 7th grader in less than one hour?
